- `sdk-event-mapper.ts` has a `prompt_suggestion` branch that yields `{ type: 'prompt_suggestion', data: { suggestions } }`
- Empty suggestion arrays are silently dropped (not forwarded)
- Non-array suggestions are silently dropped
- All three tests pass: valid suggestions, empty array, non-array
- `pnpm typecheck` passes

